com.google.cloud.firestore

Class DocumentSnapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.firestore.DocumentSnapshot

  • public final class DocumentSnapshot
extends Object
    A DocumentSnapshot contains data read from a document in a Firestore database. The data can be extracted with the getData or get methods.
